  "variable_placeholders": "Victorian brass pressure gauge authored facing south (+Z). All visible artwork follows Create's one-texture-pixel-per-model-unit density. The 32x16 custom atlas stores the front in x=0..15 and finished rear cover in x=16..31; its UV width is therefore 32. The static group contains the closed case, rear cover, front bezel, pressure fitting, dial, and fixed hub. Rotate needle around local Z at [8,9,5.3], from -135 degrees at zero pressure to +135 degrees at burst pressure. The included animation is preview-only. No frequency controls are designed into this art source.",
